00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:09,590
You didn't care before,

570
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:10,670
so don't bother me in the future either.

571
00:28:13,740 --> 00:28:14,460
Fine.

572
00:28:14,690 --> 00:28:15,840
You're not going to university, huh?

573
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,060
Okay.

574
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:18,010
Then quit school.

575
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:19,210
Just quit.

576
00:28:20,190 --> 00:28:21,270
I should sell this house

577
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,050
as soon as possible.

578
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,420
Why are you selling it?

579
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,950
Flower Street has no future.

580
00:28:27,980 --> 00:28:28,820
And the canal is in decline.

581
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,400
The house prices are dropping day by day.

582
00:28:31,750 --> 00:28:33,170
I've already inquired about it.

583
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:36,900
This house is worth at least a hundred thousand now.

584
00:28:36,930 --> 00:28:38,330
We can just live off the interest.

585
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,640
Get out!

586
00:28:39,790 --> 00:28:41,320
Get out of here!

587
00:28:41,730 --> 00:28:42,730
Let go of me!

588
00:28:42,750 --> 00:28:43,360
Wait!

589
00:28:43,470 --> 00:28:44,960
It's not your house!

590
00:28:45,710 --> 00:28:46,310
What's going on?

591
00:28:46,330 --> 00:28:47,590
Why are you arguing?

592
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:49,030
I'm not insisting on doing this.

593
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,180
Why are you getting so worked up?

594
00:28:50,210 --> 00:28:52,010
I have no intention of discussing this with you.

595
00:28:52,050 --> 00:28:53,690
This house is absolutely not for sale.

596
00:28:53,710 --> 00:28:54,750
If you want to invest,

597
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,920
use your own money!

598
00:28:55,950 --> 00:28:57,100
Have you gone crazy from being poor?

599
00:28:57,280 --> 00:28:58,920
This house was left to Siyi by Granny.

600
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,820
What right do you have to sell it?

601
00:28:59,850 --> 00:29:01,010
Siyi, don't worry.

602
00:29:01,050 --> 00:29:01,880
We're all here for you.

603
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:03,210
She can't take this house away.

604
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:04,070
We won't let her take it!

605
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:06,010
I never said I was going to take it.

606
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:08,090
I'm just trying to discuss this with her reasonably.

607
00:29:08,230 --> 00:29:09,460
Come on, you guys.

608
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:10,400
Besides,

609
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:12,290
this house belongs to my mother-in-law.

610
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:14,390
Technically, I have a right to use it.

611
00:29:14,390 --> 00:29:15,910
You've remarried.

612
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:17,560
Legally,

613
00:29:17,630 --> 00:29:19,430
Granny Ma is no longer your mother-in-law!

614
00:29:19,450 --> 00:29:20,010
That's right!

615
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:21,040
Exactly!

616
00:29:22,180 --> 00:29:23,830
Siyi is my own daughter.

617
00:29:23,910 --> 00:29:25,590
Everything I do is for her own good.

618
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:26,800
If you really want what's best for her,

619
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:27,790
just keep the house.

620
00:29:27,930 --> 00:29:29,420
Let's not talk about the financial aspect for now.

621
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:30,780
Emotionally,

622
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:32,600
this child surely can't bear to let it go.

623
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,230
Yes. Keeping this house

624
00:29:34,260 --> 00:29:36,050
will at least leave this child something to hold on to.

625
00:29:36,190 --> 00:29:37,910
No matter where she goes in the future,

626
00:29:37,910 --> 00:29:38,830
if she gets tired or feels weary,

627
00:29:38,830 --> 00:29:40,030
she'll have a place to return to.

628
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:40,530
Exactly.

629
00:29:40,670 --> 00:29:42,310
Although the rent from this house doesn't bring in much,

630
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:43,670
it's still Siyi's home.

631
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:44,670
You, as her mother...

632
00:29:44,710 --> 00:29:46,830
A home is where family is, okay?

633
00:29:46,850 --> 00:29:48,590
They are my real family!

634
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:50,350
You abandoned me

635
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,570
when I needed you the most!

636
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,830
How can you expect me to treat you as my mother?

637
00:29:57,670 --> 00:29:59,150
Blood is thicker than water.

638
00:30:00,660 --> 00:30:01,550
No matter what,

639
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:02,910
I'm still your biological mother.

640
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,580
Grandma is gone,

641
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,470
but I'm still here.

642
00:30:06,650 --> 00:30:07,640
No matter what happens,

643
00:30:07,670 --> 00:30:08,190
I won't

644
00:30:08,190 --> 00:30:09,630
leave you all alone, uncared for.

645
00:30:09,630 --> 00:30:10,390
You?

646
00:30:10,390 --> 00:30:11,270
How are you going to take care of me?

647
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,510
By selling the house, swindling all the money,

648
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:13,920
and disappearing again?

649
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:16,390
In the past, you always went to Grandma when you were in trouble.

650
00:30:16,470 --> 00:30:17,680
Now it's me.

651
00:30:17,700 --> 00:30:18,930
You have to squeeze every last bit out of me

652
00:30:18,970 --> 00:30:20,030
before you're satisfied, don't you?

653
00:30:21,940 --> 00:30:23,860
How could you say that?

654
00:30:25,090 --> 00:30:27,010
Every family has its own difficulties.

655
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:29,240
Then don't be my family!

656
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:31,290
Who asked you to?

657
00:30:33,610 --> 00:30:34,670
From now on,

658
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:36,070
you are you and I am me!

659
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:37,220
We'll live our separate lives.

660
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:38,710
No matter how difficult or tough it gets for me,

661
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:40,020
I will never ask you for help!

662
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,130
Siyi,

663
00:30:41,700 --> 00:30:43,600
you didn't even get into university.

664
00:30:44,870 --> 00:30:46,310
I'm not well-off either.

665
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,830
Who's going to support you in the future?

666
00:30:47,830 --> 00:30:48,910
I will!

667
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:55,670
From now on,

668
00:30:55,670 --> 00:30:56,750
you don't need to worry about Siyi.

669
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,760
She has me,

670
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,810
brothers and sisters,

671
00:30:58,870 --> 00:30:59,790
and the neighbors.

672
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:00,910
As long as we're here,

673
00:31:00,910 --> 00:31:02,250
we won't let Siyi suffer!

674
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:03,600
The kid is right!

675
00:31:03,690 --> 00:31:04,120
Yes.

676
00:31:04,150 --> 00:31:04,820
Exactly.

677
00:31:04,950 --> 00:31:06,160
We're all here for her.

678
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:09,060
You're all family.

679
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:11,450
You're all family.

680
00:31:11,730 --> 00:31:12,650
Is that enough?

681
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:16,580
I'm her only enemy here.

682
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:19,410
You heartless kid.

683
00:31:19,800 --> 00:31:21,280
Fine. I'll get lost.

684
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:23,870
Siwei!

685
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:25,650
Your sister finds you annoying!

686
00:31:25,860 --> 00:31:27,060
Let's get lost!

687
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:28,720
Come on, pack your things!

688
00:31:29,060 --> 00:31:30,170
Pack your things!

689
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,150
Siyi,

690
00:31:32,190 --> 00:31:34,000
don't make me leave!

691
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,280
I'll be good!

692
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:36,780
I'm not trying to make you leave.

693
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:37,910
When I get back on my feet,

694
00:31:37,910 --> 00:31:39,180
I'll come to pick you up, okay?

695
00:31:39,390 --> 00:31:40,230
No!

696
00:31:40,230 --> 00:31:41,270
I don't want to go with her,

697
00:31:41,270 --> 00:31:42,220
Siyi.

698
00:31:42,950 --> 00:31:44,030
I'm not capable enough right now.

699
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:45,630
But when I am,

700
00:31:45,630 --> 00:31:47,320
I'll come to get you, okay, Siwei?

701
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,870
No!

702
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:51,870
Pinky swear, pinky swear.

703
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:53,250
I'll definitely come.

704
00:31:54,190 --> 00:31:57,290
Cross my heart, hope to die. Stick a needle in my eye.

705
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:59,270
Take good care of yourself, okay?

706
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:02,020
I gave birth to her, and now I'm the bad guy.

707
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:04,270
Isn't it just because I'm poor?

708
00:32:05,830 --> 00:32:07,370
I'll get lost. Is that enough?

709
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,340
Stop crying!

710
00:32:11,970 --> 00:32:13,250
Take this!

711
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:14,570
Siyi!

712
00:32:14,710 --> 00:32:15,110
Let's go!

713
00:32:15,110 --> 00:32:16,310
Take good care of yourself, okay?

714
00:32:16,630 --> 00:32:17,750
Siyi!

715
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,350
I'll just pretend I never gave birth to her!

716
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:21,730
Siyi!

717
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:23,570
Let's go!

718
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:25,870
Siyi!

719
00:32:26,150 --> 00:32:27,210
Siyi!

720
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:37,300
Be careful not to step on his face.

721
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:43,100
Both of us are going to Beijing.

722
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:43,960
What about you?

723
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:45,300
I'm going to Beijing too.

724
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:46,950
To work and make money.

725
00:32:50,410 --> 00:32:52,210
You're really not going to repeat the year?

726
00:32:55,590 --> 00:32:57,300
Let's talk about the future when it comes.

727
00:32:58,220 --> 00:33:00,300
Anyway, I can't stand staying in Flower Street for even one more day.

728
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:05,760
Because of your dad?

729
00:33:08,020 --> 00:33:09,230
Now, whenever I see his face,

730
00:33:09,230 --> 00:33:10,760
I get so angry I can't hold it in.

731
00:33:11,740 --> 00:33:12,770
I'm really afraid that one day I...

732
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:18,020
Actually, your dad is pretty good to you.

733
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:20,210
He's just a bit naggy,

734
00:33:20,230 --> 00:33:20,910
but he's not a bad person.

735
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:21,790
I know.

736
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,620
But every time he's drunk, he hits my mom.

737
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:25,500
I really can't stand it.

738
00:33:28,510 --> 00:33:29,480
I tried to persuade my mom to leave,

739
00:33:29,940 --> 00:33:30,700
but she refuses to.

740
00:33:31,190 --> 00:33:31,960
Why?

741
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:35,830
Maybe she just can't let go.

742
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:36,550
I don't know either.

743
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,590
I'll go to Beijing first.

744
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:42,680
When I make some money and buy a house,

745
00:33:43,010 --> 00:33:44,130
I'll bring my mom over.

746
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:51,070
They call that capable?

747
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,340
Slow down!

748
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:55,030
The whole of Flower Street is picking on just me?

749
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,560
Hurry up!

750
00:33:56,690 --> 00:33:58,920
If you don't move fast, your sister will kick you out!

751
00:33:58,950 --> 00:34:00,350
Have you no shame?

752
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:02,810
Are you bullying me because I don't have a husband?

753
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:05,360
Siwei.

754
00:34:05,770 --> 00:34:06,570
Siwei.

755
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,800
You're picking on me alone!

756
00:34:07,910 --> 00:34:09,080
Brother-in-law!

757
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,530
What Brother-in-law?

758
00:34:10,699 --> 00:34:12,530
Let's go!

759
00:34:12,670 --> 00:34:13,949
Brother-in-law!

760
00:34:14,389 --> 00:34:15,290
What's wrong?

761
00:34:15,590 --> 00:34:16,550
I want Brother-in-law!

762
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,400
You little shameless brat!

763
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,310
