767
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:24,040
you won't be able to kiss my ass!

768
00:34:24,310 --> 00:34:25,190
What's going on?

769
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:26,429
What brother-in-law?

770
00:34:26,429 --> 00:34:27,790
Where is she taking Siwei?

771
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:29,780
You ungrateful little brat,

772
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:31,300
let's go!

773
00:34:36,120 --> 00:34:37,510
Your sister likes you, huh?

774
00:34:37,770 --> 00:34:39,139
Then go and live with her!

775
00:34:39,250 --> 00:34:39,889
Get lost!

776
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,590
Get lost!

777
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:44,310
You said it yourself.

778
00:34:44,739 --> 00:34:46,340
Brother-in-law!

779
00:34:47,650 --> 00:34:48,320
Brother-in-law!

780
00:34:48,350 --> 00:34:49,150
Come back!

781
00:34:49,429 --> 00:34:50,300
Ge Siwei!

782
00:34:50,389 --> 00:34:51,630
Come back here!

783
00:34:51,909 --> 00:34:53,429
Little brat!

784
00:34:53,449 --> 00:34:54,429
Come back here!

785
00:34:54,770 --> 00:34:55,730
Come back!

786
00:34:56,489 --> 00:34:57,520
Ge Siwei!

787
00:34:58,550 --> 00:34:59,570
Come back!

788
00:35:01,790 --> 00:35:02,480
Don't climb over!

789
00:35:02,520 --> 00:35:03,990
Get down!

790
00:35:03,990 --> 00:35:05,230
-Siwei, it's dangerous!
-Stop!

791
00:35:05,230 --> 00:35:06,950
-Siwei!
-Get down! It's dangerous!

792
00:35:06,950 --> 00:35:07,660
-Siwei!
-It's dangerous!

793
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,310
Get down!

794
00:35:09,310 --> 00:35:09,830
There's a ship!

795
00:35:09,830 --> 00:35:10,590
Don't jump!

796
00:35:20,770 --> 00:35:21,450
Siwei!

797
00:35:23,510 --> 00:35:24,270
Siwei!

798
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,790
Siwei!

799
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:33,300
Siwei!

800
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,410
Siyi!

801
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:14,100
Siyi!

802
00:36:21,630 --> 00:36:22,670
Your brother...

803
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:24,010
What happened to my brother?

804
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,310
Your brother, he...

805
00:36:28,100 --> 00:36:29,260
What happened to him?

806
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:37,630
Why did you call him?

807
00:36:37,630 --> 00:36:38,740
Auntie!

808
00:36:38,990 --> 00:36:40,270
Give me back my son!

809
00:36:40,310 --> 00:36:41,190
Auntie!

810
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,230
Auntie, calm down!

811
00:36:42,270 --> 00:36:44,630
If you hadn't called him, he wouldn't have jumped!

812
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:45,350
Calm down, calm down!

813
00:36:45,390 --> 00:36:46,910
What do you want?

814
00:36:46,910 --> 00:36:48,390
Give me back my son!

815
00:36:49,770 --> 00:36:51,140
Where's Siwei?

816
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:53,750
They're still conducting the search and recovery.

817
00:36:53,770 --> 00:36:55,840
