834
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:32,950
Auntie.

835
00:37:32,950 --> 00:37:34,510
Why did you call him?

836
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:35,660
Calm down, calm down.

837
00:37:35,870 --> 00:37:38,230
