851
00:38:15,790 --> 00:38:16,630
Are you out of your mind?

852
00:38:16,870 --> 00:38:17,910
Are you a nagging widow?

853
00:38:18,870 --> 00:38:20,270
If his mom hadn't chased after him,

854
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,610
would Siwei have jumped?

855
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,800
The root cause is his mother.

856
00:38:23,710 --> 00:38:24,270
Stop it.

857
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:34,880
Siyi,

858
00:38:35,820 --> 00:38:37,240
my mom made wontons

859
00:38:37,790 --> 00:38:38,670
with shepherd's purse filling.

860
00:38:39,630 --> 00:38:40,350
Have some.

861
00:38:45,790 --> 00:38:47,420
At least eat a little.

862
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:49,130
Otherwise, you won't be able to hold up.

863
00:38:51,250 --> 00:38:53,340
I'll have to go to the hospital to take care of you.

864
00:38:54,580 --> 00:38:56,220
Be good. Just eat ten of them.

865
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:49,100
I'm just worried she won't be able to handle it.

866
00:39:52,270 --> 00:39:53,070
Why don't we...

867
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:55,680
go down and talk to Siyi for a bit?

868
00:39:58,450 --> 00:39:59,770
What should we say when we see her?

869
00:40:04,310 --> 00:40:05,030
Then what should we do?

870
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:07,350
Fenghua is with her.

871
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:10,210
Siyi won't do anything drastic.

872
00:40:13,420 --> 00:40:14,480
Mom, hurry up.

873
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:15,610
Get me two more.

874
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:37,500
Siyi,

875
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:39,000
open the door.

876
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:45,340
Siyi?

877
00:40:49,450 --> 00:40:50,360
Siyi.

878
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,250
Have some wontons.

879
00:41:16,540 --> 00:41:17,430
I'll leave them here for you.

880
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,990
My mom said,

881
00:41:38,050 --> 00:41:39,930
if you want to cry, just cry out loud.

882
00:41:40,010 --> 00:41:41,030
Don't hold it in.

883
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,200
It's bad for your health.

884
00:41:44,300 --> 00:41:45,120
I've already cried.

885
00:41:47,410 --> 00:41:48,490
How come I didn't hear you cry?

886
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:51,790
If you don't know what to say, then say nothing.

887
00:41:54,370 --> 00:41:55,840
Let's sleep together tonight.

888
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:56,900
You can hide under the blanket and cry.

889
00:41:57,260 --> 00:41:57,780
And I'll be with you.

890
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:02,010
No need. I'm really fine.

891
00:42:02,580 --> 00:42:05,410
Stop it. You've always been like this since you were a kid.

892
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:06,800
When you're hurt,

893
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:09,010
you always keep it inside and never tell anyone.

894
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:11,430
My mom said it can cause breast cancer.

895
00:42:11,450 --> 00:42:12,780
Can I ask you a favor?

896
00:42:14,210 --> 00:42:15,130
Go ahead.

897
00:42:15,310 --> 00:42:16,420
Go out with me for a walk.

898
00:42:28,070 --> 00:42:29,240
Before the college entrance exam,

899
00:42:30,470 --> 00:42:32,590
Siwei dreamed of Grandma.

900
00:42:33,420 --> 00:42:35,010
He dreamt of her

901
00:42:35,550 --> 00:42:37,210
riding a bike with Grandpa.

902
00:42:37,960 --> 00:42:39,260
I was so angry.

903
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:41,940
Why were you angry?

904
00:42:42,450 --> 00:42:44,020
Grandma appeared in his dream

905
00:42:44,350 --> 00:42:45,430
but ignored me.

906
00:42:47,030 --> 00:42:48,670
She didn't want you to be sad.

907
00:42:49,470 --> 00:42:50,510
She couldn't bear to see that.

908
00:42:57,240 --> 00:42:58,120
Look ahead.

909
00:42:59,260 --> 00:43:00,180
Granny's gone,

910
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:01,650
but we're still here.

